{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382010/extras/image5.jpg?t=1733973231\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a powerful driving simulator-type QTE game that is experienced through realistic images.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The first-person view enhances the immersive experience, and the player must make full use of steering wheel and gas pedal controls to reach the checkpoints within the time limit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Three types of courses are available, including Metropolitan Expressway and mountain passes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382010/extras/image6.jpg?t=1733973231\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">How to play</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Steering wheel operation: Left and right arrow keys</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Accelerate: Spacebar</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Turn the steering wheel in the direction indicated by the arrow, and when the arrow disappears, step on the accelerator to move forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The key is to quickly assess the situation ahead and drive efficiently to minimize time loss.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382010/extras/image8.jpg?t=1733973231\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Reason for development</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We started development with the idea of \u201ccreating a realistic driving game that I myself would really like to play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We are thoroughly focused on the immersive visuals, realistic car behavior, driving sounds, and background music.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We designed a racing game set in Tokyo so that players can enjoy a driving experience in a virtual space that cannot be experienced in real life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382010/extras/image12.jpg?t=1733973231\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">New Course Addition: Mountain Pass Course</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A new \u201cPass Course\u201d set in the suburbs of Tokyo has been added.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The new course is set in the suburbs of Tokyo and allows players to enjoy drifting from left to right, allowing them to fully demonstrate their driving techniques.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382010/extras/image1.jpg?t=1733973231\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Racing Image  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gameover offers a wide variety of racing images for you to enjoy in each scene. The racing scenes, which allow you to fully enjoy the romance of men, will add a glamorous touch to the climax of the story.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382010/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733973231","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382010/page.bg.jpg?t=1733973231","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382010/547d41c70ff36aeffcb4e37c96e1dd33ba97e92c/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733973231","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382010/547d41c70ff36aeffcb4e37c96e1dd33ba97e92c/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733973231","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382010/extras/image5.jpg?t=1733973231\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a powerful driving simulator-type QTE game that is experienced through realistic images.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The first-person view enhance